{
  "stem": "9.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here I arrived in big America all by myself, and he asked me to come for a seder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, remember I don't know really how to read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just know more or less the alphabet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the house he lived in were some very religious people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, that service lasted about five hours, and I could not read.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All I did, I managed to read the last word on the page.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I waited until they got to that word and turned the page so he's not ashamed in front of the strangers that his niece that came from Europe doesn't know how to read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was some experience for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, anyway, going back to the seders in my childhood, there was really nothing specific that I-- I can remember about that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents had a very large family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother comes from a family I think of seven, my father at least five.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyone was married and had children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all these people perished during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the war began, one relative, who was in college about 100 miles away in the city of Lwow, could not be located.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, the Russians were killing everyone, flying very low, and killing everyone walking on the highways.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The whole family was positive that he was killed on one of those incidents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was the only one that survived the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russians took him to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was in Siberia, and he returned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody else is not here today anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's the story of my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939, Hitler decided to move east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I presume everybody knows who Hitler was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was dictator in Germany-- that Germany is in the middle of Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started occupying Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, it took just few short days.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
